      • progress

        public ListOperationCallback.PagingBahavior progress(List<E> partial)
        Override this method to handle progressive results. The user is responsible for returning a ListOperationCallback.PagingBahavior Enum to indicate whether the client should continue loading or stop.
        Parameters:
        partial - the list of resources from the current request.
        Returns:
        CONTINUE if you want to go on loading, STOP otherwise.

      • load

        public void load(List<E> result)
        This method is called by the client to load the most recent list of resources. This method should only be called by the service client.
        Parameters:
        result - the most recent list of resources.
